    "The AI tools also assist in the \"Digital Pattern Making & Virtual Prototyping\" phase.",
    "The \"Communication Framework\" facilitates the improvement of AI efficiency.",
    "Indeed, the computational collaborator is empowered to continuously readapt its model by learning from the designer's actions and feedback, thus offering fine-tuned outputs corresponding to the designer's requests.",
    "The designer's \"Contribution\" is expressed in the overall supervision of the process, in which AI capabilities are fully exploited to enhance the design results; hence, the predominant attitudes are (c-ii) \"Validation\" of the AIproduced results and (c-iii) \"In-process adjustment\" during the collaborative dynamics.",
    "Within this model, the project objectives are shared equally within the \"Collective\"."
